name: Hape Caprodon
description:
--Fig.25--
Harpe Caprodon is a creature from Eyeke, an exoplanet located 860 light years from Earth. 
They live in huge swarm of individuals on the ocean floor. They show an extreme variety of colors and types of legs, as they use what they find and merge to their body. Although their specialty is running, they can swim great distances if they need to.
